WEBVTT

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:16.660
First thing we should do is to bring peace in our life. We should become extremely peaceful. I always tell you.

00:00:18.660 --> 00:00:20.660
I agree, you have to face too many difficulties in life, but you must bring peace in life.

00:00:21.660 --> 00:00:27.660
You should give me this present on my birthday, “Shri Mataji we shall keep peace in our lives.”

00:00:27.660 --> 00:00:35.660
You should be extremely peaceful, peaceful (cool) like ice. You should be extremely tolerant. Without that it will not work out. 

00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:40.660
Even after you bear with all, you will have no problem. Everything will clear out from the Sahasrara. 

00:00:40.660 --> 00:00:45.660
Whatever you say, you bear with, all will go away (from the Sahasrara).

00:00:45.660 --> 00:00:50.660
So, it is better not to think much about it saying, I am distressed, I have this trouble etc. 

00:00:50.660 --> 00:00:55.660
 What is all this, any way!

00:00:55.660 --> 00:01:00.660
You have become saints now, what distress can you have? Can distress (or sorrow?) stay with a saint?

00:01:00.660 --> 00:01:07.660
 You should now have a conviction; now that we have become saints, 

00:01:07.660 --> 00:01:15.660
we have become very great, how can afflictions and distresses, stay with us?
We are the ones who heal others’ afflictions, like soap we wash all. How can we become dirty?

00:01:15.660 --> 00:01:20.660
Once you have this firm conviction first thing you will have, is peace. First thing, you will become peaceful within. 

00:01:20.660 --> 00:01:25.660
 And as soon as you are peaceful you will start seeing everything in the proper perspective. 

00:01:25.660 --> 00:01:30.660
So long as peace is not established within, you will not be able to see anything in the proper perspective but will see it upside down.

00:01:30.660 --> 00:01:37.660
Forming an opinion about someone, assessing a situation are such things that if your mind is upset you will not be able to see them clearly. 

00:01:37.660 --> 00:01:39.660
Hence you should have peace established within. Pray for peace. Mother has told you to be peaceful.

00:01:44.660 --> 00:01:49.660
 When you become peaceful you will understand how relationships are formed,

00:01:50.660 --> 00:01:55.660
how all joy comes, how friendships are formed, how things work out. 

00:01:55.660 --> 00:01:59.660
When you are disturbed, the angels who hover above you, all the arrangements that I have made for you- cannot understand what to do with such people. 

00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:07.660
Suddenly they are in a haste and hurry.

00:02:15.660 --> 00:02:20.660
Some people are such that they are not peevish but for everything they will say, “Where should I keep it, here or there?”

00:02:20.660 --> 00:02:25.660
 Their hands are always moving like this. It shows disturbed mind. Some persons are irritable, which is also a disturbed mind.

00:02:25.660 --> 00:02:30.660
 There is a variety of disturbed minds; some persons do not express their anger and suddenly it bursts out. 

00:02:30.660 --> 00:02:35.660
Some people become morose. Is it the sign of a saint? Saints come into the world to give.

00:02:35.660 --> 00:02:45.660
 They want to give to others. Persons who go to them should get compassion, should get love, should get satisfaction, should get protection!

00:02:45.660 --> 00:02:55.660
 And mainly, the person should feel peaceful, he should say, “I met so and so and felt so peaceful! How peaceful he himself is!” 

00:02:59.166 --> 00:03:07.762
So I have to tell you, that you might be the highest of highest, first thing [that] you have to give Me today is that in your talk,

00:03:07.762 --> 00:03:12.456
in your behavior, in your heart, you will reside one with Love.

00:03:13.634 --> 00:03:18.307
And the second thing I want to ask is that you should be peaceful people.

00:03:18.307 --> 00:03:21.919
Try to have peace with yourself. Don’t fight with yourself.

00:03:21.919 --> 00:03:25.606
Now, the western people have one problem [that] they fight with themselves.

00:03:26.581 --> 00:03:31.840
“How is it this is happening to me? I am so bad. I am no good. I have done this. I am so bad.”

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:35.087
If you go on fighting with yourself, then you will become weak.

00:03:35.377 --> 00:03:37.995
On the contrary, you must say, “I am so good. What’s wrong with me? I’ve got realization.

00:03:37.995 --> 00:03:42.438
What’s wrong with me?” Have that confidence in you,

00:03:42.438 --> 00:03:46.673
and then it will work out. And as
result of that only you start shouting at others.

00:03:47.088 --> 00:03:52.276
But supposing you understand that there is nothing wrong with you,you have to be peaceful.

00:03:52.795 --> 00:03:59.672
We all have to be very peaceful people and you have seen, My peaceful nature has solved so many problems just like that.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:03.008
So try to achieve that peace within you.

00:04:03.008 --> 00:04:05.766
That peace should not be lost at any cost,

00:04:05.890 --> 00:04:13.629
and should not be also expressed outside in a way, like I sometimes. My peace itself becomes terrible.

00:04:14.334 --> 00:04:17.754
But you don’t have that kind of a
possibility, so you just don’t do it.

00:04:18.293 --> 00:04:20.785
You just don’t do it, never do it that way.

00:04:21.055 --> 00:04:26.000
Try to be
extremely peaceful, try to make your forehead relaxed.

00:04:26.933 --> 00:04:29.777
Many people come to Me with [face] like this,  you see (distorted, twisted face), 

00:04:29.777 --> 00:04:32.508
then I just know that there is a big bhoot on the head sitting,

00:04:32.964 --> 00:04:38.169
then I shout at them. Keep your forehead relaxed, relaxed.

00:04:38.169 --> 00:04:41.831
“I am not doing anything, Mother
is doing everything. Relax, relax, relax.”

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:46.585
If you relax you’ll find that your heart will open.

00:04:47.709 --> 00:04:52.107
“My heart cannot open.” Why, why can’t you open your heart? Because

00:04:52.812 --> 00:05:02.579
you have no trust in yourself. Try to trust yourself. Open your Agnya, open your Ekadasha and your Sahasrara, and your heart will open.

00:05:03.644 --> 00:05:07.303
 Once your Sahasrara is open, your heart will open automatically,

00:05:07.822 --> 00:05:12.407
so you will have a peaceful life.
So today I am asking for two things from you.

00:05:12.801 --> 00:05:15.158
It’s a funny thing that a Mother has to ask for a gift. 

00:05:16.071 --> 00:05:20.287
And the gift you have to give – first one – is that you should be peaceful.

00:05:20.660 --> 00:05:25.708
You should express peacefulness through your own character, talking.

00:05:25.708 --> 00:05:30.396
But it doesn’t mean that you should be people who are bleak, 

00:05:30.396 --> 00:05:39.577
or who are – we can say that – are morbid people or people who tolerate nonsense.

00:05:39.867 --> 00:05:41.615
No, there is a way of resistance. 

00:05:41.615 --> 00:05:45.632
But a resistance, of a peaceful resistance, that you are
not afraid of anything;

00:05:45.632 --> 00:05:51.333
you are not frightened of anything; you are not going to bow down to anything; you are not going to compromise with anything,

00:05:51.727 --> 00:05:53.265
but you are peaceful. 

00:05:53.348 --> 00:05:59.609
That sort of a temperament you must develop and also express outside, is very important.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:20.164
If you talk to somebody sweetly, then you may get the peace of mind because you have given peace to another person.

00:06:21.626 --> 00:06:27.658
Whatever you give to another person, that you feel within
yourselves. But if you are quarrelling with another person,

00:06:27.658 --> 00:06:31.447
actually, it is the reflection of
your quarrelling nature within yourself.

00:06:32.422 --> 00:06:38.914
Today, there is a big dearth and big cry and big organizations working out the peace missions. 

00:06:39.867 --> 00:06:47.822
The peace mission is within yourself! Let us start all of us the Sahaja Yogis, who are great saints sitting here,

00:06:48.299 --> 00:06:52.046
decide today that we are going to make peace with ourselves
and with others.

00:06:52.648 --> 00:07:02.821
But first and foremost thing the peace cannot be made with quarrels. You see, like America and Russia want to decide it,

00:07:02.945 --> 00:07:04.903
with missiles – the peace part.

00:07:05.090 --> 00:07:06.449
They say: “Let’s fight out. 

00:07:07.971 --> 00:07:10.898
As many as will remain, then they can live in peace. 

00:07:10.898 --> 00:07:15.938
Let us, all those who are fighting, kill each other!” They think this is the solution of the problem.

00:07:16.546 --> 00:07:23.955
It is the other way around. Let everybody live peacefully within themselves and give peace to others,

00:07:24.492 --> 00:07:30.499
so that this peace will become a nucleus for the peace of the world.

00:07:31.371 --> 00:07:40.473
So your great task today is to establish a great source of peaceful people.

00:07:41.816 --> 00:07:43.854
We have so many Sahaja Yogis here.

00:07:45.618 --> 00:07:54.005
You’re sitting in complete peace and happiness and joy, you don’t know you are emitting all that peace, channelizing it and doing it.

00:07:54.565 --> 00:07:58.683
Now for us today to decide first of all in our hearts,

00:07:59.015 --> 00:08:05.730
that we will take to peaceful methods, when we are traveling, we will be taking to peaceful methods.

00:08:06.269 --> 00:08:15.898
Anybody who is trying to provoke you or trying to create a problem or divide you on any issue whatsoever, run away from that person 

00:08:16.043 --> 00:08:17.746
 as fast as possible.

00:08:18.913 --> 00:08:23.835
Anybody who talks of peace, the peace makers, stick on to that person.

00:08:26.172 --> 00:08:29.607
Then only you will understand that you are also getting peace.

00:08:32.888 --> 00:08:44.118
You, here, you have come to get peace, not to create problems or to listen to your problems, but to get to peace.

00:08:44.616 --> 00:08:52.631
Peace is a nature or is the quality of your Spirit.

00:08:54.211 --> 00:09:07.298
So, once you jump onto your peace, somehow, what happens that you go beyond the cause and the effect.

00:09:07.485 --> 00:09:12.916
You are beyond the cause and the effect. So the cause disappears and the effect also disappears.

00:09:15.535 --> 00:09:21.198
So, today we all have come here to worship the peace, the within and the without. 

00:09:31.967 --> 00:09:38.522
Today is the second day of our new journey 

00:09:40.667 --> 00:09:42.201
into the battlefield.

00:09:45.911 --> 00:09:52.475
We have to win people with love, compassion, affection and dignity. 

00:09:55.103 --> 00:10:03.313
When we say it’s a Vishwa Dharma, it’s a
Universal Religion we belong to, 

00:10:04.706 --> 00:10:11.307
first and foremost thing, the essence of that is peace.

00:10:13.627 --> 00:10:21.842
The peace has to be within, to begin with. You have to be peaceful within yourself.

00:10:23.438 --> 00:10:29.407
If you are not peaceful, if you are playing tricks with your ego,

00:10:32.907 --> 00:10:40.164
if you are just satisfying yourself
saying that you are peaceful, you are sadly mistaken. 

00:10:41.498 --> 00:10:44.039
Peace is to be enjoyed within
yourself.

00:10:48.375 --> 00:10:56.605
 It is to be felt within yourself. So do not give wrong satisfactions to yourself,

00:10:57.605 --> 00:11:02.347
do not give false notions to yourself. Don’t cheat yourself.

00:11:05.269 --> 00:11:10.694
Peace has to be felt within yourself, and if you are not feeling that,

00:11:10.694 --> 00:11:15.301
you shouldn’t come and ask me, “Mother, why I am not feeling it.” Because I am not going to tell you

00:11:15.301 --> 00:11:25.000
that something [is] wrong with you. You have to work it out that you should feel peaceful within yourself.

00:11:28.007 --> 00:11:34.748
It is not that if you have too much of silence outside, you feel peaceful.

00:11:36.490 --> 00:11:38.821
The peace has to be within yourself. 

00:11:41.213 --> 00:11:42.599
You have it.

00:11:42.715 --> 00:11:48.978
 Your Spirit is absolutely peaceful, ‘avyagra’, without restlessness.

00:11:49.372 --> 00:11:54.873
There is no restlessness in your Spirit, absolutely peaceful and steady.

00:11:57.909 --> 00:12:03.479
It is for you to feel it. It is not for anybody else to certify you. This is one thing.

00:12:03.977 --> 00:12:09.021
Secondly, when I am telling you something, you think I am not telling you. It doesn’t register in your brain.

00:12:09.685 --> 00:12:16.968
 You think I am telling it to X, Y, Z but not to you. You are not in it. That’s another sign [that] there is no peace.

00:12:17.424 --> 00:12:23.932
Because there is no peace, there is no registration. Whatever
goes into your head,

00:12:25.696 --> 00:12:32.351
 that is going to work out. But what I find [is] that people [who] have concave personalities,

00:12:35.318 --> 00:12:43.316
then they receive it.
Those who have convex personalities, do not register anything.

00:12:44.229 --> 00:12:52.814
The registration is so poor that, whatever I say doesn’t have any effect on them. Otherwise, whatever I say is a mantra.

00:12:52.814 --> 00:13:01.257
It should have direct effect on you, and you should feel that effect, that penetration within you.

00:13:01.900 --> 00:13:04.065
But as if it is for somebody else, 

00:13:06.021 --> 00:13:07.621
as if it is not for you. 

00:13:15.627 --> 00:13:18.859
This shows there is no peace within you.

00:13:20.823 --> 00:13:33.957
Only the peace within can register whatever is auspicious, whatever is nourishing for your growth.

00:13:36.022 --> 00:13:40.506
So try to make peace with yourself. Do not fight with yourself, 

00:13:42.863 --> 00:13:46.028
“Why should I do it?”, “I am so bad!”, “I should not have done it!”.

00:13:46.028 --> 00:13:47.687
All these things, you should not do.

00:13:49.283 --> 00:13:53.127
Try not to fight with yourself, first of all.

00:13:54.750 --> 00:14:03.793
Peace is the keynote, as I said, for universal growth of this Religion.

00:14:06.034 --> 00:14:08.104
It is disturbed by many things. 

00:14:09.030 --> 00:14:11.730
Firstly, as I said, by yourself. 

00:14:13.345 --> 00:14:17.874
You shouldn’t have funny ideas about yourself.
People have very funny ideas.

00:14:17.874 --> 00:14:24.719
I see Sahaja Yogis, as soon as they get realisation, or
something better happens to them, they start telling others

00:14:24.719 --> 00:14:34.588
how to do meditation, how to stand up, how to give bandhan, how to do this and that. It’s very very poor, is very low level. 

00:14:35.459 --> 00:14:40.883
Now the peace within expresses, first of all, [as] peace with others.

00:14:43.010 --> 00:14:50.442
 That is the first sign of
manifestation of peace. Such a person doesn’t use harsh words,

00:14:52.175 --> 00:14:54.342
doesn’t use cruel words.

00:14:56.965 --> 00:15:06.954
But he’s also not a person who is ineffective. He’s very effective, using very sweet and nice words.

00:15:07.161 --> 00:15:14.269
Maybe he begins by using harsh words, then he mellows down and comes down to a position where

00:15:14.269 --> 00:15:17.723
 he is effective as well as he is very mild and sweet.  

00:15:18.449 --> 00:15:22.245
Such a personality has to be developed outside.

00:15:23.369 --> 00:15:31.008
 So, peace with your friends, peace with
Sahaja Yogis. If you cannot be peaceful with Sahaja Yogis.

00:15:32.045 --> 00:15:35.133
 then you are no good. Absolutely no good.

00:15:37.703 --> 00:15:42.219
When you meet another Sahaja Yogi you can’t bark like dogs at each other, can you?

00:15:42.468 --> 00:15:47.755
You leave three Sahaja Yogis together, you end up with a big barking system.

00:15:50.161 --> 00:15:52.360
They can’t manage within themselves.

00:15:54.487 --> 00:16:00.321
 If there are hundred, then it’s alright. But
you can’t leave three and four here and there.

00:16:03.355 --> 00:16:05.079
So, the peace should be 

00:16:07.488 --> 00:16:15.488
with your brothers and sisters. They are all born out of My
Sahasrara and nobody has the right to insult, 

00:16:15.488 --> 00:16:17.216
to be sarcastic. 

00:16:18.907 --> 00:16:23.650
Saying things which are harmful.

00:16:27.438 --> 00:16:36.208
So that is how, our culture is going to be such that we will express complete peace within ourselves. 

00:16:37.282 --> 00:16:40.535
And you must know that you are in one body, active.

00:16:40.535 --> 00:16:43.096
You are active cells in one body. 

00:16:43.449 --> 00:16:45.290
All the cells in one body are never active.

00:16:45.290 --> 00:16:48.633
But those who are active have to be at
peace with each other, otherwise,

00:16:48.633 --> 00:16:50.733
what will happen to that poor body?

00:16:54.136 --> 00:16:55.869
So try to make peace.

00:16:57.269 --> 00:17:01.151
The second thing you can do to make peace is to talk less. 

00:17:03.051 --> 00:17:06.004
Whenever there is a quarrel or anything, just keep quiet.

00:17:06.771 --> 00:17:08.457
You see, it will have better effect.

00:17:09.130 --> 00:17:14.040
If two persons are quarrelling,
never try to solve it, but just keep quiet.

00:17:14.040 --> 00:17:19.282
Quiet is very important. More to be silent.

00:17:19.282 --> 00:17:24.315
But it should not be another extreme like English culture, that they just don’t talk, whatever it is.

00:17:28.381 --> 00:17:31.037
They just don’t talk, but they think too much.

00:17:31.597 --> 00:17:41.992
You must keep quiet with the feeling that ‘May
God bless these people some sense.”.

00:17:46.920 --> 00:17:56.502
It should not be ice frozen sea, but peace which is
effective. Peace that is effective.

00:17:57.566 --> 00:18:01.896
So in this new culture, we have to be extremely peaceful people.

00:18:02.788 --> 00:18:09.574
And that peace should be expressed on your faces. 

00:18:11.660 --> 00:18:14.413
People should understand that you are peaceful. 

00:18:16.365 --> 00:18:18.441
You are peace on this earth. 

00:18:21.702 --> 00:18:30.218
But the way peace is put into this vessel has to be clean,

00:18:30.737 --> 00:18:35.455
has to be neat and has to be placed in such a way that nothing spills out.

00:18:42.320 --> 00:18:49.153
So to have peace, the best way to put your mind right, is to think of good things.

00:18:51.808 --> 00:18:57.273
Think of the flowers, not of the thorns. What good things others have done to you.

00:18:57.273 --> 00:19:03.296
What good things there are. What are the beautiful moments you have had, and count your blessings.

00:19:06.391 --> 00:19:10.851
Count your blessings. Otherwise you cannot create peace.

00:19:13.998 --> 00:19:16.157
The another aspect

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:31.821
of peace is never try to support anything that is boisterous or which is destructive. Or also is destructive.

00:19:31.821 --> 00:19:35.600
Anything that is destructive is never to be supported.

00:19:36.554 --> 00:19:49.609
But anybody who is being tortured or aggressed or dominated, is to be protected and supported.

00:19:54.256 --> 00:19:57.905
If you have the strength of peace, you can do it just by standing there.

00:20:02.570 --> 00:20:09.339
You don’t have to fight for your
peace. But if it comes to that…

00:20:11.402 --> 00:20:15.733
A person like Hitler when he came, people had to fight for their peace.

00:20:27.857 --> 00:20:36.442
So, the first thing that was said about Christ throughout in all these music and songs you have heard now is that ‘Peace on Earth.’

00:20:39.820 --> 00:20:42.772
He came to create peace on earth.

00:20:46.184 --> 00:20:54.754
That’s only possible when you are in balance, first of all, secondly when you are Realized.

00:20:56.464 --> 00:21:01.712
Both things should be there. If only you get your Realization and there is no balance in you, 

00:21:02.413 --> 00:21:03.405
there cannot be peace. 

00:21:05.783 --> 00:21:12.692
But peace never means in any way, is a personality that recedes back,

00:21:14.082 --> 00:21:22.454
runs away from situations, escapist, who does not want to face the reality – never means that.

00:21:25.338 --> 00:21:28.268
We are creating a beautiful manger for Christ,

00:21:31.177 --> 00:21:36.208
to create the peace on earth. We have to be peaceful! 

00:21:38.948 --> 00:21:44.892
To be peaceful one has to be humble, this is the message of Christ, humble.

00:21:47.866 --> 00:21:50.593
If you become humble, peace will come.

00:21:52.718 --> 00:21:55.766
Humble is a good word, I don’t know if it explains what it means.

00:21:58.948 --> 00:22:03.692
Humble means: “Not asking for your own comfort, but comfort of others”.

00:22:04.522 --> 00:22:08.520
Out of peace comes the joy, light of joy, happiness.

00:22:09.824 --> 00:22:14.424
I wish peace for the whole world, for
the whole nations,

00:22:15.446 --> 00:22:24.718
to understand to give up all the strives, all the false battles, for money and for power,

00:22:27.144 --> 00:22:37.037
all wrong ideas that they are different from each other, and come under the banner of Sahaja Yoga 

00:22:38.475 --> 00:22:41.465
and enter into the Kingdom of God,

00:22:43.916 --> 00:22:47.619
 where they are invited with all respect and love.

00:22:49.109 --> 00:22:57.650
I wish peace to all of them, to all the countries, all the human beings, in their families, in their hearts, 

00:22:59.460 --> 00:23:00.846
with their children.

00:23:04.430 --> 00:23:06.589
With all of them, let there be peace, 

00:23:08.261 --> 00:23:11.652
Let their heart emit peace.  

00:23:13.037 --> 00:23:21.338
their tongues speak with peace, their eyes see nothing but peace.

00:23:26.942 --> 00:23:35.711
All this has to change, tremendous change has to take place, the whole universe has to take a different turn. 

00:23:36.084 --> 00:23:40.783
All that is hatred, hateful, ugly, has to vanish,

00:23:41.737 --> 00:23:43.477
and the peace has to prevail.

00:23:43.975 --> 00:23:50.000
It is not the peace of the dead but peace of the living, that has to come, of the wise.

00:23:52.374 --> 00:23:55.351
I bless all of you to be the channels of that peace,

00:23:56.643 --> 00:24:01.075
to be beautiful channels of that peace,
to be glorious channels of that peace,

00:24:03.117 --> 00:24:08.821
to be great children of your Mother, who is so proud
of you. 

00:24:09.775 --> 00:24:11.094
May God bless you.
